  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You convince Jaris to let you try his grass-cutting game, taking up the\nwhisper-thin gauzeblade and, after a deep breath, flicking it up and\ntoward a stalk of grass. A quick hiss, and the stalk\u2014along with the\nstalk directly behind it\u2014collapse, the grass on either side untouched."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u201cHuh,\u201d Jaris says. You see a flicker of grudging respect. \u201cI guess you\nknow what you\u2019re doing after all.\u201d"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "He thinks for a moment, then grins slyly. \u201cYou think you have what\nit takes to do something really tough? I hear that if someone goes\nand spends the night on Greenbriar Knoll, they have the worst\nnightmares of their life. I knew this one guy. He couldn\u2019t stop crying!\nA spiritspeaker needed to do a lot of work to help him get better.\u201d"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "He raises an eyebrow. \u201cWhat about it? I\u2019m game if you are.\u201d"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h4",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Rangers Choose"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [],
          "id": null,
          "anchor": "rangers-choose",
          "url": "#rangers-choose"
        }
      ],
      "anchor": "rangers-choose"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A) All right, Jaris. Let\u2019s do this."
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Discard all"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "icon",
              "icon": "progress"
            }
          ],
          "icon_color": "black"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and attach the"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "HELPING HAND"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "mission to Jaris."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "B) We don\u2019t have time for this."
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Discard Jaris. Each Ranger soothes 2 fatigue."
        }
      ]
    }
